About us

Stoiximan, founded in 2012, is the largest sports betting and online casino provider in Greece and Cyprus. As the leading brand in its sector, it aims to continuously evolve the gaming experience it offers to its customers and entertain sports fans in a fun and responsible way. Responsible Gaming lies at the core of Stoiximan’s mission, with a full commitment to creating a safe and secure environment for all its users.

Stoiximan has established an extensive sponsorships program, fostering a deep connection with the sporting culture and contributing to the development of sports in the two countries. Stoiximan is the main sponsor of Olympiacos FC, Panathinaikos FC, PAOK FC, APOEL FC, Apollon Limassol FC, the Stoiximan Super League, the Stoiximan GBL, the Cyprus League by Stoiximan, the Greece Men’s and Women’s Water Polo National Teams, the Cyprus Men’s Football National Team, as well as many Olympic champions.

Since its inception, Stoiximan has consistently displayed significant social contribution through various corporate responsibility programs, including Iroes, Young Heroes, Wheels of Change and Empower Forward.




Let's start with the role

We are looking for a highly analytical and data-driven Customer Insights Data Analyst to join our Customer Experience team. In this role, you will analyze customer behavior, monitor 360-degree customer data, and generate actionable insights to optimize retention, engagement, and personalization strategies. The ideal candidate will work closely with CX and BI teams to enhance customer satisfaction across all interactions and touchpoints within the Stoiximan ecosystem.







As a Customer Insights Data Analyst, you will:

Analyze customer interactions across multiple touchpoints (website, mobile app, customer support) to understand patterns of engagement, activity, and churn;
Track and analyze player behavior, including betting patterns, frequency, game preferences and habits;
Conduct post-campaign analysis to evaluate the performance of marketing campaigns, promotions, and loyalty programs;
Analyze the end-to-end customer journey to identify friction points, optimize user experience (UX), and improve conversion rates;
Translate qualitative feedback into actionable insights using text analytics to improve customer retention, product offerings, and service levels;
Provide insights into customer preferences to inform product development, feature enhancements, and new game launches;
Analyze data from customer support interactions to identify common issues, pain points, and opportunities for service improvement;
Collaborate with CRM, marketing, product, and operations teams to align customer insights with business objectives and strategies;
Ensure accurate data collection and reporting by collaborating with BI and data teams;
Present actionable insights and recommendations to senior management to support data-driven decision-making.




What you’ll bring:

Bachelor's or Master’s degree in Data Science, Statistics, Mathematics, Economics, Business Analytics, or a related field;
2+ years of experience in customer analytics & insights role or data analysis in a fast-paced environment (gaming, e-commerce, fintech preferred);
Proficiency in SQL for data extraction and analysis;
Experience with BI tools (Power BI, Tableau, Looker) and strong data visualization skills;
Experience with text analytics to provide theme segmentation & sentiment analysis;
Strong analytical skills with the ability to interpret complex data and translate it into strategic recommendations;
Knowledge of statistical modeling and predictive analytics;
Ability to work with cross-functional teams and present insights in a clear, actionable manner;
Strong attention to detail and problem-solving skills;
A proactive, can-do attitude, adaptability to changing business demands, and high drive;
Fluency in English;
Exposure to machine learning models for customer analytics is a plus;
Understanding of GDPR and responsible gaming regulations would be considered an asset.




Stoiximan Perks

🕑 Hybrid way of working;

💸Competitive salary package and bonus scheme;

👩‍⚕️ Health and life insurance for you and your family;

💰 Monthly allowance for lunch;

🏃 A buddy will support you with your onboarding;

📚 Udemy, LinkedIn learning accounts & continuous training;

⭐ Developmental 360° feedback framework.

